        </item>
        <item>
            <title>重游地铁旧观塘线过海路段  《穿越铁路秘景》第二集揭示路段仍有不断维修</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/20/mtr-45th-2/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mtr-45th-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/20/mtr-45th-2/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 07:45:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港铁]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港铁 45 周年]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港铁 45 周年活动]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[穿越铁路秘景]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1276155</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">港铁公司今日再发布《穿越铁路秘景》系列第二集，带大家重游旧观塘线过海，由蓝田站出发，进入旧观塘线路段，再穿越东区海底隧道铁路段，最后直达鲗鱼涌站，在港铁为庆祝与香港连系相伴 45 载之际，一起重温九十年代从观塘线直接过海的集体回忆。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_57452"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q5BKa4qXEX8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲穿越铁路秘景 &#8211; 重游旧观塘线过海</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>旧观塘线路段：昔日观塘线改道的城市规划印记</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">随着东区海底隧道启用，观塘线于一九八九年经东隧伸延至港岛鲗鱼涌站，直至二零零二年将军澳线正式投入服务，观塘线改道以调景岭为终点站。而由蓝田站至现行将军澳线交汇处，便成为今日的旧观塘线路段，全长约 880 米，日常载客列车从此不再驶经，旧路段现时主要保留作车长驾驶训练及让工程车行驶至各市区线车站进行维修工作。作为港铁历史最悠久的市区铁路线，观塘线在过去 45 年中见证了城市规划的演变与发展历程。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276156 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080458-694x483.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="483" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080458-694x483.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080458-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲观塘线于一九八九年经东隧伸延至港岛鲗鱼涌站（图片来源：港铁新闻稿）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276157 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2002-499x580.jpg" alt="" width="499" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2002-499x580.jpg 499w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2002.jpg 774w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 499px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲直至二零零二年将军澳线正式投入服务（图片来源：港铁新闻稿）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276158 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080550-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080550-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080550-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲观塘线改道以调景岭为终点站（图片来源：港铁新闻稿）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>茶果岭露天段</strong><strong>：重遇东隧收费广场前的景致</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">在旧观塘线路段的中段位置，就是茶果岭露天段，它位于东区海底隧道收费广场巴士站旁，昔日的乘客途经此处可一览车外景色。随后便进入旧路段与现行将军澳线交汇处，然后进入东区海底隧道，最后直抵鲗鱼涌站。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276159 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276161 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲茶果岭露天段（图片来源：港铁新闻稿）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276160 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241120at-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241120at-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241120at.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲旧路段与现行将军澳线交汇处（图片来源：港铁新闻稿）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong></strong></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/20/mtr-45th-2/life-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
